  RollerCoaster Tycoon 3: Wild! invites tycoons of all ages to create and
  manage a safari-themed adventure park featuring all new white-knuckle rides
  and a host of prowling, untamed beasts.

  animal shows and petting zoos, and characters such as a new VIP, an
  AnimalKeeper staff member and the Tiger mascot - an RCT favorite.
  The new Show Ride editor also allows players to recreate the wilderness for
  a Safari Train Adventure or Paddle-Steam Cruiser. Players can choreograph
  animal shows using the RCT MixMaster; test out their tranquilizer dart
  shooting prowess to recapture an escaped animal, and increase their cash
  flow through new shops and billboards.
